 keep the finger on the pulse of society.<\\/p><p>Welcoming the participants, the Artsakh Republic Security Council Secretary Samvel Babayan noted the importance of the youth involvement in the sociopolitical life of Artsakh, noting that the position of each of them can determine the policy of the country\'s authorities.<\\/p><p>During the meeting, Samvel Babayan answered the questions of the participants concerning the activities of the security council and the security council office, its liabilities and functions, historical and political significance of the Artsakh national-liberation movement, the struggle for survival, security and defense of the Armenians, the Azerbaijani-Karabakh conflict in the context of regional developments and other issues.<\\/p><p>At the end of the meeting, Samvel Babayan called on young people to always be ready for challenges, redouble their efforts to overcome difficulties, effectively solve problems, and keep in mind that responsibility and initiative should be proportional in any situation.<\\/p>\"}', '2020-09-09 00:00:00', '2020-09-11 00:00:00'),
